1
00:00:00,499 --> 00:00:03,260
Do you like stories?
你喜欢听故事吗?

2
00:00:03,784 --> 00:00:07,325
I want to tell you a true story.
我想要告诉你一个真实的故事.

3
00:00:08,088 --> 00:00:12,546
It happened to a friend of mine a year ago.
这是一年前发生在我的一个朋友身上的故事.

4
00:00:12,997 --> 00:00:23,070
While my friend, George, was reading in bed, two thieves climbed into his kitchen.
当我的朋George治在床上看书时,两个小偷爬进了他的厨房.

5
00:00:23,487 --> 00:00:29,618
After they had entered the house, they went into the dining room.
他们进到屋里后,走进了饭厅.

6
00:00:29,634 --> 00:00:35,881
It was very dark, so they turned on a torch.
饭厅里很暗,于是他们打开了手电筒.

7
00:00:36,082 --> 00:00:41,139
Suddenly, they heard a voice behind them.
突然他们听到身后有声音.

8
00:00:41,445 --> 00:00:45,405
What's up? What's up?' someone called.
“什么事?什么事?”有人叫着.

9
00:00:46,081 --> 00:00:54,002
The thieves dropped the torch and ran away as quickly as they could.
小偷扔下了手电筒,以他们最快的速度逃走了.

10
00:00:54,216 --> 00:00:59,816
George heard the noise and came downstairs quickly.
乔治听到了响声,迅速地下了楼.

11
00:00:59,929 --> 00:01:04,817
He turned on the light, but he couldn't see anyone.
他开了灯,但不见一个人.

12
00:01:04,818 --> 00:01:08,045
The thieves had already gone.
小偷们已经逃走了.

13
00:01:08,324 --> 00:01:13,048
But George's parrot, Henry, was still there.
但是George的鹦鹉Henry仍在那里.

14
00:01:13,049 --> 00:01:16,036
What's up, George?' he called.
“什么事,George?”它叫着.

15
00:01:16,224 --> 00:01:20,724
Nothing, Henry,' George said and smiled.
“没事,Henry.” George笑着说,

16
00:01:20,810 --> 00:01:22,760
Go back to sleep.'
“接着睡觉吧.”

